acceptance_criteria: "After pm init . in an empty dir, the next pm command (e.g. pm list) works without --pm-path; discovery accepts cwd/ancestor as tracker root when it holds a valid tracker layout OR init . is redefined to the workspace-discovery spelling with an explicit flag for raw-root mode (decision recorded); tracker_not_initialized recovery bundle probes for a cwd-rooted tracker and emits an executable --pm-path next step when found; no second tracker can be silently created at .agents/pm when a cwd-rooted tracker exists; e2e test covers the init-then-list round-trip for both init modes; GH-501 closed with a comment linking the fix"
